                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             and his sister-in-law Henrietta -, confirmed the evidence of 
               <persName id="t17741019-64-person539">
                  Catharine
                   Macmullon
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person539" type="surname" value="Macmullon"></interp>
