            .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17741019-64-person540">
                  Thomas
                   Jeffs
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person540" type="surname" value="Jeffs"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person540" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person540" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the parish officer, proves nothing; says the surgeon is dead, that examined the body;<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177410190030"></xptr> it is so long ago forgets what marks were on the body.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17741019-64-person541">
                  Thomas
                   Byrne
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person541" type="surname" value="Byrne"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person541" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person541" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
