            . 
               <persName id="t17741019-64-person542">
                  Richard
                   Powers
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person542" type="surname" value="Powers"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person542" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person542" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             told me that he had given 
               <persName id="t17741019-64-person543">
                  Mary
                   Cuddy
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person543" type="surname" value="Cuddy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person543" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person543" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             a kick while she lay upon the hearth.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you understand him that that was the cause of her death?</p>
               <p>Byrne. No, he merely shoved her with his foot to ask what she did there.</p>
               <p>The prisoners, in their defence, called 
               <persName id="t17741019-64-person544">
                  Hugh
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person544" type="given" value="Hugh"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person544" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             M'Mabon, who swore that 
               <persName id="t17741019-64-person545">
                  Mary
                   Cuddy
               <interp inst="t17741019-64-person545" type="surname" value="Cuddy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person545" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-person545" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was not in the room while the prisoners were there.</p>
               <p>MACMARNE <rs id="t17741019-64-verdict290" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-verdict290" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-64-verdict290" type="verdictSubcategory" value="manslaughter"></interp>
               not guilty of the murder, but guilty of manslaughter
            </rs>. <rs id="t17741019-64-punish291" type="punishmentDescription">
